<h3>Will I lose weight on a juice cleanse?</h3>
<p>Weight-loss often occurs on the cleanse, but isn't the sole focus, nor the goal of our cleanse. Think of it as a full body reset, prompting your body to re-balance itself. During a cleanse, usually whatever you need to balance out in your body will occur. When given the proper nutrition, our bodies naturally adjust to maintain our ideal weight, effortlessly and instinctively.</p><br>
